        </para>
        <para id="id2259501"><m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mo>•</m:mo></m:math> Bayes versus minimax, and linear versus non-linear estimations
(Chapter 11).</para>
        <para id="id2259517"><m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mo>•</m:mo></m:math> Wavelet bases
