        <para id="id2259563"><m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mo>•</m:mo></m:math> Minimax optimality
(Chapter 11).</para>
        <para id="id2259580"><m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mo>•</m:mo></m:math> Model selection for denoising in redundant dictionaries
(Chapter 12).</para>
        <para id="id2259596"><m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mo>•</m:mo></m:math> Compressive sensing
(Chapter 13).</para>
